# Switch Allocation

| Switch   | Function                   |
| -------- | -------------------------- |
| SW[7:0]  | 8-bit Data Input           |
| SW[11:8] | RAM Address Input          |
| SW12     | Program Mode Select        |
| SW13     | Sensor/Input Source Select |
| SW14     | Clock Speed Select         |
| SW15     | Demo Program Select        |

## Details

```text
SW[7:0]   -> Instruction/Data Value

SW[11:8]  -> RAM Address

SW12 = 0  -> Manual Programming Mode
SW12 = 1  -> CPU Execution Mode

SW13 = 0  -> Switch Input
SW13 = 1  -> Sensor Input

SW14 = 0  -> Slow Clock
SW14 = 1  -> Fast Clock

SW15 = 0  -> Multiplication Demo
SW15 = 1  -> Add/Sub Demo
```

