# Push Button Allocation

| Button | Function      |
| ------ | ------------- |
| BTN0   | Program Write |
| BTN1   | CPU Run       |
| BTN2   | System Reset  |
| BTN3   | Input Enter   |

## Details

```text
BTN0 -> Write Instruction/Data into RAM

BTN1 -> Start CPU Execution

BTN2 -> Reset CPU, Registers,
        Program Counter,
        Control Unit and Flags

BTN3 -> Provide User Input
        during IN/INS Instruction
```

